					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"I thought it might be all show and no substance, but he’s put plenty of meat on this plate.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"原本我还想摆盘大概比较重视外观，开始吃了之后才发现肉其实放得还挺多的。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
